{"tid":928661,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"Pizzahut 大批縮水?","createTime":"2018-12-05T04:11:01.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-06T04:30:28.000Z","uid":116614,"like":0,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"13cf44ff78c1ef96de4c3c6b66d3ce02ad2ccc57","tid":928661,"uid":116614,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-05T04:11:01.000Z","msg":"早幾日上朋友屋企開枱<br />\n咁不嬲夜晚都會叫pizzahut<br />\n如是者叫左個千島海鮮(大批)<br />\n送到上嚟發現裝pizza個盒仲細過裝粉麵湯嗰個盒<br />\n咁我地就心諗 乜大批12吋咋咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n打上去問 佢就話係佢地cut得衰 話送多個上嚟<br />\n咁5條友完全唔夠食 等到佢送上黎 一樣係12吋size <br />\n有冇巴打知道係幾時縮水嫁?"},{"pid":"80a5c46540ebeee34e4fb57261000a934e363dee","tid":928661,"uid":193192,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-05T04:42:14.000Z","msg":"縮左水好多年 <br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/news/art/20091010/13298051\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fnews%2Fart%2F20091010%2F13298051&d=9dLtHruvR2BPlGDk%2Bu2xir%2BHiWCy6q6AsXO%2BLNmzhis%3D&h=f12e0d74\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fnews%2Fart%2F20091010%2F13298051&h=32f863d0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/news/art/20091010/13298051</a>"},{"pid":"ce8d3b25d630bc43f663ab871bcf66c13045dd03","tid":928661,"uid":172844,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-05T05:07:43.000Z","msg":"#2條片都咁多年啦<br />\n我都未入去做<br />\n<br />\n我做左5年左右啦<br />\n都冇話換過個pizza pan<br />\n大批嚟講厚餅12吋  芝心同薄就13吋 (好似係   唔記得了)<br />\n同埋pizza盒大唔過個卡通tray係正常嘅<br />\n因為要撐大個卡通tray先放得落d盒仔同湯<br />\n再唔係有個情況就係粒dough發得唔靚縮咗水照出"},{"pid":"e711b2b9662b152c059797fb399b791fc2da9886","tid":928661,"uid":194281,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-05T13:19:30.000Z","msg":"個人餐都無鬼埋,垃圾唔會幫襯"},{"pid":"a29451e5b5b6828eb3e0b10f721669a2686c4238","tid":928661,"uid":44333,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-06T04:30:28.000Z","msg":"咁食邊間好"}]}